        <title>Deepin配置使用ibus输入引擎</title>
        <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/linux/install_ibus/</link>
        <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2019 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
        
        <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/linux/install_ibus/</guid>
        <description>&lt;img src="http://localhost:1313/posts/linux/install_ibus/D736D06C-7B39-4813-A96D-027E2A5F8D2D.png" alt="Featured image of post Deepin配置使用ibus输入引擎" /&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;1安装&#34;&gt;1、安装
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;sudo apt install -y ibus ibus-gtk ibus-gtk3 ibus-qt4&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;2使用-im-config-切换输入法引擎&#34;&gt;2、使用 im-config 切换输入法引擎
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/posts/linux/install_ibus/810DAEA8-E19F-4186-A9BE-0BA8FC6792A4.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1086&#34;
	height=&#34;557&#34;
	srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/posts/linux/install_ibus/810DAEA8-E19F-4186-A9BE-0BA8FC6792A4_hu11267401714580170078.png 480w, http://localhost:1313/posts/linux/install_ibus/810DAEA8-E19F-4186-A9BE-0BA8FC6792A4_hu5984764086862442013.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
