		data-flex-basis=&#34;467px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;直接一路确定、yes&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/posts/linux/install_ibus/2C8C3069-1C1F-430E-9C47-71D1399D6601.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1086&#34;
	height=&#34;557&#34;
	srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/posts/linux/install_ibus/2C8C3069-1C1F-430E-9C47-71D1399D6601_hu1922163122108971443.png 480w, http://localhost:1313/posts/linux/install_ibus/2C8C3069-1C1F-430E-9C47-71D1399D6601_hu8086688541406285619.png 1024w&#34;
